title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 9 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 9 2022
description:
Alaska Senator Dan Sullivan joins Clay and Buck to discuss the truckers, SCOTUS and the military vax mandate. Boris Johnson declares the end of covid restrictions in the U.K. "Harm reduction": Psaki defends Biden's free crack pipe program. The root cause of the drug problem is the open southern border. California mandated masks and Arizona didn’t, so why did both states have exactly the same covid surge? A caller engages C&B as the show closes.
